  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/bda1289ed9bf7dd9344e3667cd138ba2.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1560 height=93 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Survival is not a choice, but a struggle!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>iZolated </strong>throws you into the epicenter of post-apocalyptic chaos. There are no heroes here, only those who managed to find bullets and clean water.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/057c617e0a6891b5b924b39ed4c6f932.poster.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/057c617e0a6891b5b924b39ed4c6f932.webm?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/057c617e0a6891b5b924b39ed4c6f932.mp4?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A harsh open world where the slightest mistake costs you your life. Find gear, engage in fights, and prove that you are the top of the food chain in this chaos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/bda1289ed9bf7dd9344e3667cd138ba2.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1560 height=93 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/c6538bbd609072931277fc9815578015.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1560 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A vast world full of dangers hides valuable resources. But remember: the more valuable the loot, the higher the risk. Items do not lie in the same places. Each new world is different from the previous one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/a89db20f8487af12de4099246b8985bc.poster.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/a89db20f8487af12de4099246b8985bc.webm?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/a89db20f8487af12de4099246b8985bc.mp4?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/7c020105c8463f15eb989acfc94e8b75.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1560 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Each weapon is unlike the others. Your arsenal—your rules. Don’t limit yourself to basic stats: find and apply unique modifiers to turn an ordinary gun into the perfect survival tool.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/67539a34a31247dc856231a651b56ad8.poster.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/67539a34a31247dc856231a651b56ad8.webm?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/67539a34a31247dc856231a651b56ad8.mp4?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/0ad5cb207a0b066725fcb30ddd4ee0bf.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1560 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Your life depends on what you find under your feet. Collect weapons and tools literally from trash.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/a4039f3b14548fed6e27285855d2616d.poster.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/a4039f3b14548fed6e27285855d2616d.webm?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/a4039f3b14548fed6e27285855d2616d.mp4?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/4b8df44c44a610c57be916414ff40052.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1560 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Weather and day-night cycles are not just decorations. They are factors that can kill you faster than enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/8c2a7bf14b1d5c011d211a6c25f66b78.poster.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/8c2a7bf14b1d5c011d211a6c25f66b78.webm?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/8c2a7bf14b1d5c011d211a6c25f66b78.mp4?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/9f52d023303e2785ab523e8377204077.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1560 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fog, acid rain, and magnetic storms will keep you on your toes. They will turn the rules of the game upside down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/c83c45772353b83a222c2bf40a514e5c.poster.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/c83c45772353b83a222c2bf40a514e5c.webm?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/c83c45772353b83a222c2bf40a514e5c.mp4?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/bda1289ed9bf7dd9344e3667cd138ba2.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1560 height=93 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Are you ready for a real challenge?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/f7f0fceca62f0aa5ae4abe74f46e3d75.poster.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/f7f0fceca62f0aa5ae4abe74f46e3d75.webm?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/f7f0fceca62f0aa5ae4abe74f46e3d75.mp4?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/bda1289ed9bf7dd9344e3667cd138ba2.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1560 height=93 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/bda1289ed9bf7dd9344e3667cd138ba2.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1560 height=93 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Survival is not a choice, but a struggle!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>iZolated </strong>throws you into the epicenter of post-apocalyptic chaos. There are no heroes here, only those who managed to find bullets and clean water.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/057c617e0a6891b5b924b39ed4c6f932.poster.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/057c617e0a6891b5b924b39ed4c6f932.webm?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/057c617e0a6891b5b924b39ed4c6f932.mp4?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A harsh open world where the slightest mistake costs you your life. Find gear, engage in fights, and prove that you are the top of the food chain in this chaos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/bda1289ed9bf7dd9344e3667cd138ba2.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1560 height=93 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/c6538bbd609072931277fc9815578015.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1560 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A vast world full of dangers hides valuable resources. But remember: the more valuable the loot, the higher the risk. Items do not lie in the same places. Each new world is different from the previous one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/a89db20f8487af12de4099246b8985bc.poster.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/a89db20f8487af12de4099246b8985bc.webm?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/a89db20f8487af12de4099246b8985bc.mp4?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/7c020105c8463f15eb989acfc94e8b75.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1560 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Each weapon is unlike the others. Your arsenal—your rules. Don’t limit yourself to basic stats: find and apply unique modifiers to turn an ordinary gun into the perfect survival tool.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/67539a34a31247dc856231a651b56ad8.poster.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/67539a34a31247dc856231a651b56ad8.webm?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/67539a34a31247dc856231a651b56ad8.mp4?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/0ad5cb207a0b066725fcb30ddd4ee0bf.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1560 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Your life depends on what you find under your feet. Collect weapons and tools literally from trash.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/a4039f3b14548fed6e27285855d2616d.poster.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/a4039f3b14548fed6e27285855d2616d.webm?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/a4039f3b14548fed6e27285855d2616d.mp4?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/4b8df44c44a610c57be916414ff40052.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1560 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Weather and day-night cycles are not just decorations. They are factors that can kill you faster than enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/8c2a7bf14b1d5c011d211a6c25f66b78.poster.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/8c2a7bf14b1d5c011d211a6c25f66b78.webm?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/8c2a7bf14b1d5c011d211a6c25f66b78.mp4?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/9f52d023303e2785ab523e8377204077.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1560 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fog, acid rain, and magnetic storms will keep you on your toes. They will turn the rules of the game upside down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/c83c45772353b83a222c2bf40a514e5c.poster.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/c83c45772353b83a222c2bf40a514e5c.webm?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/c83c45772353b83a222c2bf40a514e5c.mp4?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/bda1289ed9bf7dd9344e3667cd138ba2.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1560 height=93 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Are you ready for a real challenge?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/f7f0fceca62f0aa5ae4abe74f46e3d75.poster.avif?t=1773939968\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/f7f0fceca62f0aa5ae4abe74f46e3d75.webm?t=1773939968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799360/extras/f7f0fceca62f0aa5ae4abe